page_title: How to work with prompt engineering and the Completion API
page_description: Learn how to work with the Completion API for prompt engineering.
chunk_title: Repeat the instructions at the end
chunk_content: Repeat the instructions at the endModels can be susceptible to recency bias, which means that information at the end of the prompt might have more significant influence over the output than information at the beginning of the prompt. Therefore, it's worth experimenting with repeating the instructions at the end of the prompt and evaluating the impact for your use case.We saw in the earlier example how repeating the instruction at the beginning and the end of the prompt leads to a higher likelihood of getting an accurate model response.
